data.description: Welcome to Foxhaven! You will enjoy the 1.19 acres of partial open land and woods for privacy! This Cape Cod offers 3 bedrooms & 1 full bathroom. You will walk into a nice family room, & then a eat in kitchen with new stainless appliances- refrigerator, smooth cooktop range - both only a few months old, dishwasher (2022), washer & dryer (2023)- a new deck off the kitchen thru a sliding door with plenty of sunlight. 2 bedrooms on the first floor with a full bathroom with recent remodeling to include new fixtures, & flooring, second floor offers a large 3rd bedroom & an open room making this a nice sitting area- suite-office area. Roof was installed 2016 - with a 50 year warranty, the HVAC unit is a Trane that is 5 years old - a new storage shed with new well pump also. Enjoy the corner lot near public landing with boat access to the York River- great for kayaking also &enjoying the wildlife of herons, spotted sandpipers, great black-backed gulls, &bald eagles. Sand beach & picnic area.
